00:11:28.896 --> 00:11:32.686 A:middle
of making diners happy
because it gives them a way

00:11:32.686 --> 00:11:34.866 A:middle
to let us know if
they're satisfied or not.

00:11:36.096 --> 00:11:38.826 A:middle
By the same method we
can also exclude features

00:11:38.826 --> 00:11:40.146 A:middle
that do not serve our goals.

